Requirements
============

For running the test suite, the following packages are needed:

  * The nose testing framework
    Debian and Ubuntu: python-nose
    Source: http://code.google.com/p/python-nose/

  * The pymox stub/mock utilities (version 0.5.3 required)
    Debian and Ubuntu: python-mox
    Source: http://code.google.com/p/pymox/

  * The unittest2 package (or Python >= 2.7)
    Debian and Ubuntu: N/A
    Source: http://pypi.python.org/pypi/unittest2

  * For coverage reports, the Python coverage package
    Debian and Ubuntu: python-coverage
    Source: http://pypi.python.org/pypi/coverage

And, to increase coverage of scrobble.py, please ensure "psutil" is
available.


Running tests
=============

Tests are run via the Makefile:

  % make test      # Runs all unit tests
  % make coverage  # Creates a coverage report in the "coverage" subdirectory
